article:
This is a 'list of submachine guns' with articles available on Wikipedia.
Because the exact definition of a submachine gun can vary much from source to
source it includes assault rifles chambered for submachine gun or pistol
cartridges, some machine pistols, and personal defense weapons (PDWs), all of
which are sometimes designated as submachine guns.
